    {
      "name": "1. Authentication - Registration Flow",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Step 1 - Initiate Registration (Send OTP)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Response indicates success\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.message).to.include('OTP');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "console.log('âœ… Registration initiated. Check your email for OTP.');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{test_email}}\",\n  \"name\": \"Test User\",\n  \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"role\": \"OWNER\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register/initiate",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register", "initiate"]
            },
            "description": "**Purpose**: Initiate user registration and send OTP to email\n\n**Request Body**:\n```json\n{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"role\": \"OWNER\" // or \"VET\"\n}\n```\n\n**Expected Response**:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"OTP sent to your email. Please verify to complete registration.\"\n}\n```\n\n**Note**: Check email inbox for OTP code (valid for 5 minutes)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Step 2 - Complete Registration (Verify OTP)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Registration successful and token received\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.token).to.exist;",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.userId).to.exist;",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.email).to.exist;",
                  "    ",
                  "    // Store token for future requests",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', jsonData.token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('user_id', jsonData.userId);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('user_email', jsonData.email);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "console.log('âœ… Registration complete! Token saved to collection variables.');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{test_email}}\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\",\n  \"name\": \"Test User\",\n  \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"role\": \"OWNER\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register/complete",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register", "complete"]
            },
            "description": "**Purpose**: Complete registration by verifying OTP\n\n**Request Body**:\n```json\n{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\",\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"role\": \"OWNER\"\n}\n```\n\n**Expected Response**:\n```json\n{\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"userId\": 1,\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"role\": \"OWNER\",\n  \"message\": \"Registration successful\"\n}\n```\n\n**Note**: Token is automatically saved to collection variables"
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Two-step registration process with OTP verification"
